org.bukkit.block.data.type

Interface Sapling

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BlockData, Cloneable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Bamboo

    public interface Sapling
extends BlockData
    'stage' represents the growth stage of a sapling.
    When the sapling reaches getMaximumStage() it will attempt to grow into a tree as the next stage.
